object(Connection)#4 (3) {
  ["dsn":"Connection":private]=>
  string(5) "MyDsn"
  ["username":"Connection":private]=>
  string(10) "MyUsername"
  ["password":"Connection":private]=>
  string(10) "MyPassword"
}
Done!
